f*g\in\mathscr{S}
 \begin{align} \left|x^\alpha(f*g)^{(\beta)}(x)\right| &=\left|x^\alpha\left(f^{(\beta)}*g(x)\right)\right|\\ &\le G\max\left(C_{\alpha,\beta}\left|\frac{x^\alpha}{(x-R)^\alpha}\right|,C_{0,\beta}\left|x^\alpha\right|\right)\\ &\le G\max(C_{\alpha,\beta},C_{0,\beta})(R+1)^{|\alpha|} \end{align} 
